%F A037302 a(n) = ((n-1)^2)!*A078524(n)/(n^(n-1)*A078525(n)). - _Andrew Howroyd_, Apr 11 2020
%e A037302 a(2)=1: The polytope of 2 X 2 matrices is the line segment from (1,0;0,1) to (0,1;1,0), with length v(2)=2, so a(2) = 1! * 2 / 2^1 = 1.
